parameters.name: PROTON_FLUX_1
parameters.description:
Pulse-height analyzed proton flux for particles from                 
                        1.829 - 2.045 MeV. A value of -9.99999e+10 is a missing data value.

parameters.name: STD_DEVIATION_1
parameters.description:
Column contains the statistical error in the associated with         
                        PROTON_FLUX_1
